OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStarting with patchy cloud and
OL,6,Fbright spells, and perhaps a few light
OL,7,Fshowers. Then becoming dry with bright
OL,8,For sunny spells, before cloud
OL,9,Fincreases. Outbreaks of rain will
OL,10,Fspread east this afternoon, perhaps
OL,11,Fnot reaching Kent by late afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain this evening, clearing
OL,14,Feast by the early hours. Large amounts
OL,15,Fof cloud and showers or longer spells
OL,16,Fof rain will follow, perhaps locally
OL,17,Fheavy. Milder than previous nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
