OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FStarting with showers or
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain, possibly heavy
OL,7,Fat times, most likely across eastern
OL,8,Fareas. Drier and brighter conditions
OL,9,Fthen spread follow, along with
OL,10,Fscattered showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fsunshine and scattered sometimes heavy
OL,14,Fshowers. Rain and strong winds arrive
OL,15,Fovernight, clears Tuesday with breezy
OL,16,Fconditions and showers following.
OL,17,FWednesday lighter winds, mainly dry
OL,18,Fwith sunny spells, warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
